    <h4><a href="http://www.fortuneconferences.com/mpwlondon-2012">Most Powerful Women: London</a></h4>
    <h5>June 18, 2012 : London UK  </h5>
    <p>The inaugural <em>Fortune</em> Magazine Most Powerful Women international meeting and gala dinner will bring together the most prominent European women leaders in business, along with selected leaders from government, media, philanthropy, government, and the arts. Participation is by invitation only. 
</p>
      </div>
    
  <div class="item">
